  <summary date="2017-04-25T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Commends Holocaust education activists on their efforts to include Holocaust education in states' public school curricula.

Urges more states to enact legislation mandating Holocaust education in their schools.

Expresses the sense of the House of Representatives that more should be done to instill in the nation's future the promise that we will never forget the horrors of the Holocaust and must always work to prevent such atrocities from occurring in the future.</summary>
